snippet.title: MINESHAFT - Alex and Steve Life (Minecraft Animation)
snippet.description:
Alex and Steve venture into the mysterious depths of an abandoned mineshaft when an earthquake opens up a massive ravine in a nearby village. Through exploring its secrets, the pair are tasked with locating the cause of the disaster. After undergoing a series of separate adventures, Alex and Steve must band together to eliminate any further threats.
